msg: BZ 58309: ISAPI: Update bundled pcre from version
- Add an entry to NOTICE
- drop unneeded HAS_PCRE and PCRE_STATIC defines
from isapi Makefiles. HAS_PCRE was not used and
PCRE_STATIC is already set in iis/pcre/config.h.
- drop dfatbles build no longer needed fro 8.37
- Use original pcre 8.37, added Windows build files
- pcre.x86, pcre.amd64, pcre.ia64 (nmake)
- pcre.dsp (MSVC GUI build)
- config.hw
- When doing another update the pcre.* build
files should be stable as long as no new files
or file renames appear in pcre. The config.hw
should be stable as long as the original
file config.h.generic is stable.
